# Day 7 – KQL Basics

## Learn Syntax

### Example Query

```
SigninLogs
| where ResultType != 0
| project TimeGenerated, UserPrincipalName, IPAddress
```

### Operators

* where
* project
* limit
* distinct
* count

## GitHub Post

```
Day-07-KQL-Basics.md
```

Add **10 example queries**.

