# Day 8 – Aggregation Queries

## Learn

* summarize
* bin()
* count()

### Example – Brute Force Detection

```
SigninLogs
| where ResultType != 0
| summarize FailedAttempts=count() by IPAddress, bin(TimeGenerated,5m)
| where FailedAttempts > 10
```

